                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/49606",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=neck",
                        "name": "neck",
                        "displayName": "Sylvain DIDELOT",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I can confirm this bug. Happens when error controller takes over after an exception is thrown for example.\r\n\r\nFix is easy:\r\n{code}\r\ndiff ContextSwitch.php ContextSwitch.php.bak \r\n283c283\r\n<                 $response->setHeader($header, $content, true);\r\n---\r\n>                 $response->setHeader($header, $content);\r\n{code}",
